title: Recognizing Your Value | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Recognizing Your Value | Joel Osteen
description:
Your value doesn’t come from people or success; it comes from your Creator. You are a child of the Most High God!


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
